items.title: Stabbing, liquid toss attack in Japan rubber factory injures 15
items.description: Fourteen people were injured in a stabbing attack in a factory in central Japan in which an unspecified liquid was also sprayed, authorities said.

items.title: U.S. launches Christmas Day strikes on ISIS targets in Nigeria, Trump says
items.description: The strikes come after President Trump spent weeks accusing the West African country's government of failing to rein in the persecution of Christians.
